  "description": "<p><strong>数字风暴(Digital Storm)刚刚推出了其首款轻薄型Haswell游戏笔记本——配备了13.3英寸的全高清屏幕的VELOCE。</strong>该机的厚度仅有1.26英寸(3.2CM)，采用了高端的英特尔酷睿i7-4800MQ处理器和Nvidia GTX 765M显卡。13.3英寸的屏幕拥有1920x1080的分辨率，全背光键盘四周则采用了冷银灰的配色。机器内部还有两个硬盘驱动器(mSATA和2.5')，支持RAID功能。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e7d8d24/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244268.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DDigital+Storm%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE13.3%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Haswell%E8%BD%BB%E8%96%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E6%9C%AC\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244268.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DDigital+Storm%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE13.3%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Haswell%E8%BD%BB%E8%96%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E6%9C%AC\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244268.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DDigital+Storm%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE13.3%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Haswell%E8%BD%BB%E8%96%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E6%9C%AC\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244268.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DDigital+Storm%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%BE13.3%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B8Haswell%E8%BD%BB%E8%96%84%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E6%9C%AC\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244268.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%